MLJ WorkFlow ### 2.1 define models 需要定义三个模型: 1. pca model 2. clustering model 3. classficiation model ::: {.cell execution_count=3} ``` {.julia .cell-code} PCA = @load PCA pkg=MultivariateStats KMeans = @load KMeans pkg=Clustering SVC = @load SVC pkg=LIBSVM model=PCA(maxoutdim=2) # pca model model2 = KMeans(k=3) # clustering model model3 = SVC() # svm dodel ``` ::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stderr} ``` [ Info: For silent loading, specify `verbosity=0`. [ Info: For silent loading, specify `verbosity=0`. [ Info: For silent loading, specify `verbosity=0`. ``` ::: ::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout} ``` import MLJMultivariateStatsInterface ✔ import MLJClusteringInterface ✔ import MLJLIBSVMInterface ✔ ``` ::: ::: {.cell-output .cell-output-display execution_count=4} ``` SVC( kernel = LIBSVM.Kernel.RadialBasis, gamma = 0.0, cost = 1.0, cachesize = 200.0, degree = 3, coef0 = 0.0, tolerance = 0.001, shrinking = true) ``` ::: ::: ### 2.2 PCA 在 PCA 流程中要完成两步: 1. PCA 模型训练(如果为了便于可视化, 维度为 2或者 3) 2. 将原始数据映射到降维的空间上 ::: {.cell execution_count=4} ``` {.julia .cell-code} mach = machine(model, Xtr) |> fit! Xproj =transform(mach, Xtr) first(Xproj,10) ``` ::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stderr} ``` [ Info: Training machine(PCA(maxoutdim = 2, …), …). ``` ::: ::: {.cell-output .cell-output-display execution_count=5} ```{=html}
